    "CS = cross sectional.",
    "High dosage = all private or mostly private, Low dosage = some private or each year private.",
    "Small sample corrections are used.",
    "When df < 4, Tipton (2015) notes that the normal approximation fails, and p values should be interpreted with caution.",
